@startuml
title Frontend - Certificados Component (high level)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "Certificados.jsx" as Certificados
component "Registros.jsx" as Registros
component "Reportes.jsx" as Reportes

Certificados -> Registros : reads sacramento data
Certificados -> Reportes : (optional) request aggregated stats

note right of Certificados
  - Renders certificate template
  - Injects `CERT_CSS` into print/export
  - Helpers: isMatrimonio(), getSpouseNames()
  - Export: html2canvas + jspdf
end note

@enduml
